Just run a small webserver like caddy (doesnt have to be, but that is what im using) on your machine listening to port `43110` on localhost, so that when someone doesnt have a proper link,

Improper link, hardcoded to be `127.0.0.1:43110/ZiteURL`
Proper link, softcoded to match `/ZiteURL`

my config 
```
:43110 {
	redir http://192.168.0.110{uri}
}
```
to be fair, i have it setup to listen on port 80 by a webserver on the zeronet thing so...

